.frame-block
  .site-container
    .container
      .title.__absolute Frame
      .relative-container
        img.block-spacer.__no-padding(src='../build/img/pages/index/bg-spacer.png')
        //.video-scroll-block - это контейнер, который реагирует на wheel и проигрывает видео внутри себя
        .video-scroll-block
          .video-container
            .top-line
            //В data-duration выводим продолжительность видео
            video(data-src='../build/img/pages/index/frame.mp4',
            preload='auto',
            muted='muted',
            data-poster='../build/img/pages/index/frame-poster.jpg',
            data-duration=5.034667)
            .bottom-line
          .carbon.lozad.__frame
            .line
            .text CARBON MADE FRAME WITH LIGHT WEIGHT
            .line
      .text-block
        p The City Racer gives you back your city. With its strong performance, CARBO GATTO leaves everything behind them. The slender design provides for true pleasure of driving and even brings a smile to the faces of first-time motorbike riders.
